        </div>
        <div
          id="touch-base"
          class="help-suggestion my-2 flex flex-row items-center justify-between border-b border-stone-700/20 py-4
            dark:border-stone-300/20">
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <h4 class="font-chinook text-stone-700 dark:text-stone-100">
              Questions and answers
            </h4>
            <p class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-300 opacity-80 text-base">
              If there's anything we can try and help you with we will. Let us know what you need in the form and we'll do our best to
              answer.
            </p>
          </div>
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="icon icon-tabler shrink-0 ml-8 icon-tabler-arrow-big-right-lines rotate-90 text-stone-500 md:rotate-0"
